The '''Troll''' is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is found in the [[Cavern of Earth]], and around certain [[town]]s, such as [[Onrac]] and [[Lufenia (Final Fantasy)|Lufenia]]. In sprites and concept art the Troll is shown clutching its head. A friendly soul of a Troll in the [[Whisperwind Cove (Final Fantasy)|Whisperwind Cove]] dungeon in [[Soul of Chaos (Final Fantasy)|Soul of Chaos]] moans about its head aching. This refers to some folklore on trolls saying they suffer from a constant ringing in their ears.

